&gt; set
&gt; &gt; user-agent-field and e-mail-adress at the settings-tab) - put in
&gt; your seeds
&gt; &gt; 11. on the frontpage of the UI click &#39;start crawling pending jobs&#39;
&gt; &gt; 12. enjoy
